{"tid":1113273,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"每次聽到印刷術，都有一種自悲","createTime":"2019-04-17T22:11:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-17T22:29:12.000Z","uid":232575,"like":0,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"d74109069645af388926b5da934865495448f1ee","tid":1113273,"uid":232575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T22:11:10.000Z","msg":"讀中學個陣己經話獨專儒術既<span style=\"color: green;\"><ins>選士制度</ins></span><span style=\"color: red;\"><ins>重文輕理</ins></span>，<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>儒學以外知識受到嚴重局限</strong></span>。短期有教化道德既作用，但長遠來講會令士子只識<span style=\"color: purple;\">四晝五經</span>吟詩作對而無常識。<br />\n<br />\n係史學角度，雕版印刷始於隋唐，活字印刷術既發明時間為宋代。<span style=\"color: red;\"><ins>現代(華)人藉此贊揚華夏傳統智慧。我很大程度不同意</ins></span>，因為我認為印刷術早於秦漢已經出現。<br />\n<br />\n有打三國無雙都知道漢代已有<span style=\"color: green;\"><ins>傳國玉璽--即係皇帝「印」章</ins></span>，叫得印章，我就視它為印刷術<span style=\"color: red;\"><ins>。秦朝(前221年－前207年）與北宋（960年&mdash;1127年)相距1000年</ins></span>，終於有一位<span style=\"color: green;\"><ins>畢昇（?&mdash;1051年）發明「活字印刷術」</ins></span>。<br />\n<br />\n而活字印刷由元朝西傳，第一部活字印刷機由一名<span style=\"color: green;\"><ins>天主教傳教士</ins></span>台約爾(Samuel Dyer，1804年－1843年）發明，<span style=\"color: red;\"><ins>全世界第一本由活字印刷機印刷既係</ins></span><span style=\"color: purple;\">「聖經」</span>。<br />\n<br />\n一件物件或者技術出現咗1000年以上都無人發展，最後重要由「藩屬國」發揚光大。<ins>[green]我所感到既唔會係自豪而係自悲，因為活字印刷<span style=\"color: red;\">唔係反映</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">華夏智慧</span><span style=\"color: red;\">而係反映</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">華夏輕視知識</span>既結果。</ins><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nReference:<br />\n<a href=\"https://kknews.cc/history/9mnx4bq.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fkknews.cc%2Fhistory%2F9mnx4bq.html&d=hObUr7UKzm7jHRUyz9oMSJggdM0W6%2BkgeusliPwa7Y4%3D&h=d8c2c414\" target=\"_blank\">https://kknews.cc/history/9mnx4bq.html</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://kknews.cc/zh-hk/history/meon8a2.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fkknews.cc%2Fzh-hk%2Fhistory%2Fmeon8a2.html&d=hObUr7UKzm7jHRUyz9oMSJggdM0W6%2BkgeusliPwa7Y4%3D&h=18d3816d\" target=\"_blank\">https://kknews.cc/zh-hk/history/meon8a2.html</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chiculture.org.hk/tc/china-five-thousand-years/846\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchiculture.org.hk%2Ftc%2Fchina-five-thousand-years%2F846&d=hObUr7UKzm7jHRUyz9oMSJggdM0W6%2BkgeusliPwa7Y4%3D&h=5eb50702\" target=\"_blank\">https://chiculture.org.hk/tc/china-five-thousand-years/846</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://bdcconline.net/en/stories/dyer-samuel\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbdcconline.net%2Fen%2Fstories%2Fdyer-samuel&d=hObUr7UKzm7jHRUyz9oMSJggdM0W6%2BkgeusliPwa7Y4%3D&h=a0edeaa7\" target=\"_blank\">http://bdcconline.net/en/stories/dyer-samuel</a>"},{"pid":"fc51f2476de70d97b69bc1f7b006d6dcdca42e5c","tid":1113273,"uid":173852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T22:29:12.000Z","msg":"學界其實唔當印章係印刷術，頂多只係源頭"}]}